lead_paragraph: Nicole Broch Larsen of Denmark and Sweden's Camilla Lennarth took a two-stroke, second-round lead Friday at the Australian Ladies Masters.

headline.print_headline: Larsen, Lennarth Take 2nd-Round Lead at Ladies Masters
